德国拉姆斯坦公司 (Rammstein) 的蒂尔·林德曼 (Till Lindemann) 起诉德国媒体涉嫌不当行为报道https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammsteins-till-lindemann-sues-german-outlet-for-alleged-misconduct-reporting-3781643?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rammsteins-till-lindemann-sues-德国涉嫌不当行为举报渠道Liberty DunworthWed, 07 Aug 2024 10:01:16 +0000 Music NewsNews..Metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3781643 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是由于该出版物报道了 2023 年对他提出的不当性行为指控</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammsteins-till-lindemann-sues-german-outlet-for-alleged-misconduct-reporting-3781643">《Rammstein》的蒂尔·林德曼 (Till Lindemann) 起诉德国媒体涉嫌不当行为报道的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rammstein">德国拉姆斯坦</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/till-lindemann">蒂尔·林德曼 (Till Lindemann)</a>对一家德国新闻媒体提起诉讼，此前该媒体报道了去年对他提出的不当性行为指控。</p><p>针对这位德国创作型歌手的指控首次出现于 2023 年 5 月，当时一名女粉丝在社交媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammstein-deny-till-lindemann-drink-spiking-allegation-3450675">声称自己在演出前的派对上被毒打</a>。</p><p>这位来自北爱尔兰的歌迷谢尔比·林恩(Shelby Lynn)随后向 <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-northern-ireland-65843882" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>声称，她在维尔纽斯演出后被招募并“诱骗”与这位歌手发生性关系。林恩说，她的饮料在演出中被下了毒，但澄清说她没有受到性侵犯。</p><p>从一开始， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammstein-deny-till-lindemann-drink-spiking-allegation-3450675">林德曼和他的乐队成员就否认了所有指控</a>，而这位歌手的法律团队则称这些指控“无一例外都是不真实的”。</p><p>下个月，德国媒体<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammsteins-till-lindemann-now-under-investigation-in-germany-after-sexual-assault-allegations-3456457" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Tagesschau</em>发表了一份报告，其中包含其他女性的新指控</a>，所有这些指控都指控主唱性侵犯。这一说法再次被林德曼和乐队否认，但这仍然导致了严重的后果。 </p><figure id="attachment_3781648" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3781648" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3781648" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270.jpg" alt="德国拉姆斯坦乐队 (Rammstein) 的蒂尔·林德曼 (Till Lindemann) 现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Till-Lindemann@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3781648" class="wp-caption-text">德国拉姆斯坦乐队 (Rammstein) 的蒂尔·林德曼 (Till Lindemann) 现场表演。图片来源：Santiago Bluguermann/LatinContent 来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>鉴于这些指控， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rammstein-respond-after-till-lindemann-dropped-from-book-publisher-amid-drink-spiking-and-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3451686">这位主唱在受到指控后被他的图书出版商 Kiepenheuer &amp; Witsch 解雇</a>，柏林检察官办公室对涉嫌事件展开了调查。该项目后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/police-drop-sexual-misconduct-investigation-into-rammsteins-till-lindemann-3490375">于 2023 年 8 月结束并被放弃</a>。</p><p> “新闻报道中证人的陈述尚未得到调查证实，”检察官办公室当时表示（来自<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rock/till-lindemann-rammstein-responds-sexual-misconduct-allegations-1235748227/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a> ）。林德曼后来在社交媒体上分享了一份声明，其中写道：“我感谢所有公正等待调查结束的人。”</p><p>现在，在柏林检察官办公室的调查被撤销一年后，乐队对德国出版物<em>《明镜周刊》</em>的高管提起诉讼。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://loudwire.com/till-lindemann-sues-news-outlet-potential-forgery-fraud-coverage-sexual-misconduct-allegations/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Loudwire 报道</a></em>，这位歌手已向汉堡检察官办公室对《明镜周刊》的高管提起刑事诉讼，指控该刊物的报道包含伪造文件以及企图进行审判欺诈。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">新闻发布<br />雷·蒂尔·林德曼<br /><br />由于《明镜》在针对蒂尔·林德曼的禁令程序中提交的宣誓书，对《明镜》高管提出伪造和企图审判欺诈的刑事指控<a href="https://t.co/3tfk2VsIng">pic.twitter.com/3tfk2VsIng</a></p><p> — 谢尔茨·伯格曼 (@schertzbergmann) <a href="https://twitter.com/schertzbergmann/status/1819296524410511428?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>就在乐队在网上发表声明后发布的，解释了这些指控在过去一年中对他们的影响。</p><p> “自去年夏天以来，我们一直在积极处理针对乐队的指控。我们非常严肃地对待这一争议，即使其中大部分是毫无根据且过度夸大的。这是一个将伴随我们很长一段时间的内在过程。我们每个人都以自己的方式做这件事，并以不同的方式处理它，”它写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-S3vK5IrYm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244